a motion picture about you.

1231
01:19:14.521 --> 01:19:17.148
- Motion picture?
- Oh.

1232
01:19:18.149 --> 01:19:21.069
Well, that's something like television.

1233
01:19:22.362 --> 01:19:24.239
Without commercials.

1234
